{
  "texts": [
    "Amin et al.",
    "(Amin et al. 2020b) put forth an automated approach that facilitated the discrimination between cancerous and non-cancerous brain MRI scans.",
    "Various methods were employed for the segmentation of potential lesions.",
    "Following segmentation, a feature set was selected for each identified lesion, incorporating factors such as shape, texture, and intensity.",
    "Subsequently, an SVM classifier was applied, employing diverse cross-validation strategies on the feature set to gauge the efficacy of the proposed framework."
  ]
}